_sText:
This is my second map.  It is a random hostage spawn map.  Please provide feedback.  

Thanks to all the wonderful tutorials posted by members of fpsbanana.  I could not have learned what I know without them.  

I hope this map is well received.  I will make other versions of this map if requested.  I have considered making a de map version. Please feel free to provide feedback positive or negative. I am always interested in learning more.

Last note.  Please do not use my textures or remake my map without my permission.  I hope you enjoy the map.
